OL,3,CBill on Assisted Dying faces key vote
OL,4,Cat Scottish Parliament
OL,6,FThe MSP seeking to change the law and
OL,7,Fintroduce assisted dying for
OL,8,Fterminally ill Scots has insisted an
OL,9,F"overwhelming majority" of Scots back
OL,10,Fthe measure.
OL,12,FLiam McArthur spoke out ahead of his
OL,13,Fmember's Bill facing a key vote at
OL,14,FHolyrood on Tuesday.
OL,16,FThe Bill, brought forward by the
OL,17,FLiberal Democrat MSP would, if passed
OL,18,Fallow adults at the advanced stage of
OL,19,Fa terminal illness to seek help to end
OL,20,Ftheir life.
