OL,3,CBill on Assisted Dying faces key vote
OL,4,Cat Scottish Parliament
OL,6,FSpeaking ahead of Tuesday evening's
OL,7,Fvote, the MSP insisted: "This an issue
OL,8,Fon which an overwhelming majority of
OL,9,Fpeople of Scotland believe a change in
OL,10,Fthe law is required.
OL,12,F"Public polling is consistent across
OL,13,Fage range, political affiliation,
OL,14,Fdisability status, geographic area and
OL,15,Freligious belief ` Scots want to see
OL,16,Fdying people in this country given
OL,17,Fmore choice at the end of life."
