OL,6,FHe added: "Drawing on international
OL,7,Fevidence, my Bill would ensure people
OL,8,Fwho meet the strict eligibility
OL,9,Fcriteria are able to exercise that
OL,10,Fchoice in a way that is robustly
OL,11,Fsafeguarded.
OL,13,F"Indeed, my Bill would put in place
OL,14,Fsafeguards that don't currently exist,
OL,15,Fa situation that leaves many
OL,16,Fterminally ill people more vulnerable
OL,17,Fand more likely to take matters into
OL,18,Ftheir own hands.
