OL,6,F"This shows that not taking action has
OL,7,Fserious consequences, too, with more
OL,8,Fdeaths that are painful and
OL,9,Fundignified, despite the best efforts
OL,10,Fof palliative care, and more
OL,11,Ftraumatised families left behind."
OL,13,FIf his Bill passes on Tuesday evening,
OL,14,Fthe proposals would return to Holyrood
OL,15,Ffor further scrutiny and amendment,
OL,16,Fbefore MSPs have a final vote on
OL,17,Fwhether it should become law.
