OL,6,FMr McArthur, however, insisted that
OL,7,FScotland "cannot put off" debating
OL,8,Fassisted dying, and the Parliament
OL,9,F"cannot continue to leave this issue
OL,10,Fin the too difficult box".
OL,12,FHe said that MSPs "must, at the very
OL,13,Fleast, allow time for amendments to be
OL,14,Fconsidered to see if a Bill can be
OL,15,Fagreed that commands majority support
OL,16,Fand public confidence".
OL,18,FHe added: "To my MSP colleagues, I
OL,19,Fsay, if you have not yet made up your
OL,20,Fmind, my door is always open.
